<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>MoveBot</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#020817;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* NAVBAR */

nav{
width:100%;
height:90px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:0 60px;
background:rgba(2,8,23,0.92);
backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.08);
position:fixed;
top:0;
left:0;
z-index:1000;
}

.logo h1{
font-size:46px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.logo p{
font-size:14px;
color:#84ffff;
margin-top:4px;
}

nav a{
text-decoration:none;
color:white;
font-size:18px;
transition:0.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
color:#00ffee;
}

/* HERO */

.hero{
width:100%;
min-height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:160px 80px 80px 80px;
gap:60px;
}

/* LEFT */

.left{
width:50%;
}

.left h2{
font-size:92px;
line-height:0.95;
font-weight:bold;
}

.gradient{
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00ffbb,#00d9ff);
-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.line{
width:130px;
height:4px;
background:#00ffee;
border-radius:20px;
margin:30px 0;
}

.left p{
font-size:20px;
line-height:1.9;
color:#d4d4d4;
max-width:700px;
}

/* BUTTONS */

.buttons{
margin-top:40px;
display:flex;
gap:20px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.btn{
padding:16px 30px;
border-radius:50px;
border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.18);
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
color:white;
font-size:16px;
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
transition:0.3s;
cursor:pointer;
}

.btn:hover{
transform:translateY(-5px);
border-color:rgba(0,255,255,0.4);
box-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(0,255,255,0.15);
}

/* RIGHT */

.right{
width:50%;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
}

.card{
width:420px;
height:420px;
border-radius:40px;
background:radial-gradient(circle at center,
rgba(0,255,200,0.18),
rgba(0,0,0,0.2));

border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.12);

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;

box-shadow:0 0 70px rgba(0,255,255,0.08);

backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
}

.card .emoji{
font-size:120px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.card h3{
font-size:54px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.card p{
font-size:16px;
letter-spacing:1px;
color:#b8ffff;
}

/* FEATURES */

.features{
padding:100px 90px;
}

.section-title{
font-size:62px;
margin-bottom:50px;
}

.feature-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
gap:28px;
}

.feature-card{
padding:35px;
border-radius:30px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.08);
backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
transition:0.3s;
}

.feature-card:hover{
transform:translateY(-6px);
border-color:rgba(0,255,255,0.25);
}

.feature-card h3{
font-size:30px;
margin-bottom:18px;
}

.feature-card p{
font-size:17px;
line-height:1.8;
color:#d4d4d4;
}

/* FUTURE */

.future{
padding:100px 90px;
}

.future-box{
margin-top:40px;
padding:50px;
border-radius:35px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.08);
}

.future-box p{
font-size:20px;
line-height:2;
color:#d4d4d4;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{
padding:40px;
text-align:center;
font-size:16px;
color:#98e9e9;
border-top:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.08);
}

/* MOBILE */

@media(max-width:1100px){

.hero{
flex-direction:column;
text-align:center;
padding-top:140px;
}

.left,
.right{
width:100%;
}

.left h2{
font-size:64px;
}

.line{
margin:auto;
margin-top:25px;
margin-bottom:25px;
}

.buttons{
justify-content:center;
}

.card{
width:340px;
height:340px;
}

.card .emoji{
font-size:90px;
}

.card h3{
font-size:40px;
}

}

@media(max-width:700px){

.left h2{
font-size:48px;
}

.section-title{
font-size:42px;
}

.features,
.future{
padding:80px 30px;
}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->

<nav>

<div class="logo">
<h1>MOVEBOT</h1>
<p>Smarter Movement Awareness</p>
</div>

<a href="#">Bot Ecosystem</a>

</nav>

<!-- HERO -->

<section class="hero">

<div class="left">

<h2>
MOVE<br>
SMARTER.<br>
<span class="gradient">LIVE BETTER.</span>
</h2>

<div class="line"></div>

<p>
MoveBot is an awareness-driven mobility assistant focused on encouraging healthier and more sustainable movement choices. It promotes walking awareness, smarter short-distance travel, reduced fuel wastage, and conscious transportation habits.
</p>

<div class="buttons">

<button class="btn">
🚶 Walking Awareness
</button>

<button class="btn">
🌍 Sustainable Travel
</button>

<button class="btn">
⚡ Smarter Daily Movement
</button>

</div>

</div>

<!-- RIGHT -->

<div class="right">

<div class="card">

<div class="emoji">🚶</div>

<h3>MOVEBOT</h3>

<p>
Move Better • Live Better
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->

<section class="features">

<h2 class="section-title">
<span class="gradient">Core Features</span>
</h2>

<div class="feature-grid">

<div class="feature-card">
<h3>🚶 Walking Awareness</h3>

<p>
Encourages walking for short distances to improve health and reduce unnecessary fuel consumption.
</p>
</div>

<div class="feature-card">
<h3>🌍 Sustainable Mobility</h3>

<p>
Promotes environmentally responsible movement habits and smarter transportation decisions.
</p>
</div>

<div class="feature-card">
<h3>⚡ Daily Movement Insights</h3>

<p>
Creates awareness about everyday movement choices and their long-term impact on health and sustainability.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FUTURE -->

<section class="future">

<h2 class="section-title">
<span class="gradient">Future Vision</span>
</h2>

<div class="future-box">

<p>
Future versions of MoveBot may include QR-based awareness systems, smart movement tracking, route awareness, camera-assisted transportation recognition, and sustainable travel guidance systems designed to improve urban mobility awareness through ethical and preventive technology.
</p>

</div>

</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

<footer>

MOVEBOT • Part of Bot Ecosystem

</footer>

</body>

</html>
